videos.headline: Spartans DE blocks early field goal
videos.description: Michigan State DE Demetrius Cooper doesn't even have to jump to block Central Michigan PK Brian Eavey's 45-yard field goal attempt.

videos.headline: Michigan State WR dives for beautiful grab
videos.description: Spartans QB  Connor Cook throws a deep pass to WR Macgarrett Kings Jr. for a 42-yard gain against Central Michigan.

videos.headline: Michigan State blocks another field goal
videos.description: Spartans DE Shilique Calhoun stays on his feet and still manages to block Central Michigan kicker Brian Eavey's 43-yard field goal attempt.
